blog.description: Clone wars was such a huge part of my life because it gave me an escape when I needed it most. Let’s have fun and celebrate together!!! Share your ocs and headcanons and we can scream together!!

summary: When Taya heard there was a litter of loth cats she knew it would be a perfect way to heal Thumper’s lovesick heart. When...
caption:
When Taya heard there was a litter of loth cats she knew it would be a perfect way to heal Thumper’s lovesick heart. When thumper saw the little thing curled up on a blanket he was SOLD! Taya told him not to worry about regulation and that she would take care of all the paperwork (by that she means Jace will) it isn’t until they are about to leave that her eyes start to itch and a sneeze threatens to release. 

Thumper loves little mittens and she literally becomes the mascot for their squadron. All of the clones love her (but she always sleeps on Thumper’s chest when it’s time for bed.) This is the beginning of a very fuzzy friendship :)

(THANK YOU SO MUCH @anyakinskywalker FOR DESIGNING MITTENS AND LETTING THUMPER ADOPT HER xD!!!! I guessed on your jedi’s color scheme but she was so fun to draw!! excited to see more of your oc’s journey!! Taya and Thumper would be happy to help her anytime she needed!!))
